Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天  他擊出的那一記球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如離弦之箭  直衝雲霄…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  逆轉本壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想勝過我隊不可撼動的第四棒世界級的蓋茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是再去練個一百年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思鳴海  借我1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天  吸引住我的便是那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被球場的藍天吞噬的棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也不過是在說遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在線棒球遊戲  Power Play ball
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱PWRB  我是完全沉迷在其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這遊戲對網上選手信息儲存量實在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是當下還是過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從鼎鼎大名到無名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要輸入名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能創建參數與之相對應的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門了  快給我走人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  請不要影響到其他客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫…老大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  要輕輕地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  是你要委託我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我向井均一生的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們目無王法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租金上漲25個點  簡直太無法無天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為無法無天  我們才是黑社會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吧  少校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我堅決要談判到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓這店變成小鋼珠店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢不錯嘛  小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群怪傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧  要不打個賭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用賭博一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們贏了那租金就維持不變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要是贏了  你們就快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這提議怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…就用那個比如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也喜歡棒球的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受你的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼定了  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就能和你們一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢  現在怎麼也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要準備場地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場…地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體日期改日聯絡你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.52,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}那個夏天的二十一球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏面盡失  我向井均一生的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我也被拉到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您屈駕到鄙店真是對不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  為了我這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼話  西村先生的店就像我們的家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了的話  我們可不干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥也說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你哥哥是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿俊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個很擅長格鬥遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來最近很少見到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們該怎麼辦呢  少校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  人數不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將可不能算為戰鬥力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行  棒球根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  算上玫歐也只有六人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  玫歐完全不懂棒球的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成連我也算在內了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣姑且…能打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要取勝的話  有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練由我來擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  在那個夏天最後的日子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們練起了棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺  時光飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}一棒 明老闆   二壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}二棒 阿宏     中場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}三棒 阿哲     三壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}四棒 巖男     左外場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}五棒 第四代   投手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}六棒 西村先生 游擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}七棒 少校     捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}八棒 電桿     右外場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}九棒 玫歐     一壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}教練  愛麗絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}及其助手and候補 鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海這都是你的錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代的那對相差懸殊組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責教育的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我要練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我人生中重要的一部分被浪費掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  要說到他們倆對我話的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有進壘和回壘這兩個手勢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本隊的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城東高中棒球部  這不是名門高中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是參加了高中田徑聯賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都不是等閒之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛麗絲  這人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  明天好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  事到如今可別說要放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫老大以前打過棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此還曾出戰甲子園的王牌選手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是勝利投手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你們就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見你們這種玩玩遊戲打打電動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得自己是在打棒球的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨不得想捏碎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲子園又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的高中主勝投手你記得幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個都不記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天一過就沒他們什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像垃圾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球不會變成錢  所以我拋棄了它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已  做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了吧  藤島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善喜哥做的  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你們一個人情  僅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明知道根本的實力還敢和他比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果比賽中玫歐受傷的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將  過來熱身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣她不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  教練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲  你真打算在這裏指揮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是對方球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽與空氣都是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我決不逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你逃避得已經夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯哥  來一記漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去磨練男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二好球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球  三振出局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  不愧是雛村哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是接下來的擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本喜一在高二是背負著王牌號碼的投手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗於準決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後他就自主退學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相尚不明確
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過根據當時的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本與暴力組織開辦的賭球有關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能調查到的就只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是30年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相早已被掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本喜一到底是個怎樣的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投出了怎樣的球  流了多少汗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又給他留下了怎樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都無從考證了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家所遺忘了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  看見這個手勢的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是完全沒記住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  給我防好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不投球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌先保留實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過威懾力十足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢小瞧我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力  努力  NEET
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  NEET
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…NEET可不可以別叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}NEET泰迪熊隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  跑者開始跑壘了  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽就像這樣不斷進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們NEET泰迪熊隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是臨時拼湊的卻也打得有聲有色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球  打者出局攻防轉換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那傢伙快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲我還是留在後頭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要讓你做替補兼教練助手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看過第四代的病歷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來他現在的身體狀況就很不適合打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得快點讓他別打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不是言聽計從的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最大的問題是根本喜一到底什麼時候投球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說了好戲會留在後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這投手的球路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據他一直以來所投出的球能分析出來個大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根本的則是未知數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有他以前的投球記錄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這已經是30年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕連數據庫都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這說不定只是我一廂情願的無謀賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明所以地就這樣毫不猶豫地跑了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定還會有人記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你急死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  快點把那逞強的傢伙帶進車裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  怎麼能交給你們這些毫無控球能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點交換場地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我會順利地把你們全幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球  打者出局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿宏  兩萬賭我能打到球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  我賭兩倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟錢扯上關係的時候  我可是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟麻將可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  我這就去磨練男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送一壘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我磨練了男子氣概了  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人出局  一壘有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園藝部的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來代打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  我怎麼能代替第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  藤島中將
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的  鳴海小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我代打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太矮了我看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  你在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判  快點開始比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球區是由打者的體格來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  身體嬌小的愛麗絲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球區的範圍會縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二好球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揮棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三好球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收回你的判決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在看哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不死三振
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:17:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著到你了 鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聰明的招數我可不會再上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算從第一球就開始試著打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像就眼力還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就這點能耐的話可就沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還挺能撐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 你是想說從那垃圾遊戲里鍛煉出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對尼莫老大來說那說不定只是個無聊的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也該來認真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一球  就用這球結束這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在  鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  逆轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是再見本壘打哦  藤島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  我真的太崇拜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我追隨你一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真走運呢  下次和我一起去賭馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道我的決勝球會投指叉球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看了記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經是30年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說記錄了 怎麼連投球策略都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在尼莫老大討厭的那個遊戲里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲裏怎麼會有我的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是記得尼莫老大的人們做的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是30年前親眼見過尼莫老大投球並銘記在心的人寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過輸了就是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租金就維持不變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來愛麗絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐也會輸真少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上這次現在是十連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方隊伍的隊服很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這強敵是個女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也能玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來  沉迷PWRB的似乎並不只是我們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長  生意興隆真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前那騷動  客人們都蠻擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  他來過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏的哥哥回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也拉開了新事件的序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我來說也是個不祥的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前理所當然的事即將被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:26.91,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}翻譯:絆笑    Miya　校對:千葉命 特效:我們的夏天　後期:毛球/阿爽/whwdlxy9416
